summary: WE WILL NOT FAIL - Today, as Elon Musk interviews Donald Trump on X, we introduce the "We Will Not Fail Hat" coin. This special token is a tribute to Trump’s slogan in his return video on the X network, a message of unshakable strength and courage in the ultimate environment for free speech. We Will Not Fail Hat captures that same energy on the Ethereum network, serving as a reminder of the importance of resilience and the power of freedom.
